                        <div class="text_page_path_title">
                            <h2>10. Children's privacy</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text_page_path_desc">
                            <p>TrustActivity does not knowingly collect or solicit any information from anyone under the age of 13 on this Service. In the event that we learn that we have inadvertently collected personal information from a child under age 13, we will delete that information as quickly as possible. If you believe that we might have any information from a child under 13, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@trustactivity.com" class="blue_text" target="_blank">support@trustactivity.com</a>.</p>
